dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Dedication to the king in the bottom right corner. Includes the Savoy and Dauphine coat of arms. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 36 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_title_s: Carte et description generale de Dauphiné: avec les confins des pais Provinces voisines; le tout Racourcy et reduict par Jean de Beins ingenieur et geographe du roi.; Carte et description generale de Davphine
